cast.overview: One day at work, unsuccessful puppeteer Craig finds a portal into the head of actor John Malkovich. The portal soon becomes a passion for anybody who enters its mad and controlling world of overtaking another human body.
cast.title: Being John Malkovich

details.biography:
She was born Feb. 24, 1962, in Eugene, to Charles and Norma Day Wetzell. She married Gerald E. Stephen on Aug. 12, 2000, in Tigard. She died Nov. 22, 2009 of cardiac arrest. She was 47.

Judi graduated from Clatskanie High School and received a master's degree from the University of Oregon. She was a teacher and an actress.
details.name: Judith Wetzell
